title: The 90s Hip Hop 25 (Dancing Man's Guide to Music)
description:
Nothing but Hip Hop classics of the 90s - from 91 to 99, west coast to east coast, jazz rap to hardcore. This is not meant for the already addicted hip hop heads who'll have all or most of this; this is for those knowing there is something to get but not getting it yet.
